Memes have started dropping on social media networks following the Constitutional Court's judgement that former president Jacob Zuma has been sentenced to 15 months' imprisonment for defying an order to appear before the Zondo Commission. ALSO READ | BREAKING | Zuma sentenced to 15 months imprisonment by ConCourt Social media went crazy after Constitutional Court Justice Sisi Kampepe delivered Zuma's judgement, with many poking fun at the former president's fate. Some pitied Zuma, even offering to serve his sentence for him.      